  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York Metro-North Railroad Lines, 2009 is a line theme representing the Railroad tracks and service lines of the Metro-North Railroad system with the exception of the Port Jervis and Pascack Valley Lines. Attribute data includes the names of the lines and length of the segment.. Raw data was acquired from files from the New York State Department of Transportation. Data is provided in the projection NAD83 to align with the NYCMap basemap. The realigned data has not been thoroughly checked for accuracy."
